{"tid":796650,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"炒黃牛算唔算係古惑仔最重要嘅收入來源？","createTime":"2018-08-28T02:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T03:28:40.000Z","uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"653086505044f8aaa33575bdbe59bcc624ade36c","tid":796650,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"排隊買劉德華演唱會門票被斬案 警拉黑底「拓海」<br />\n<br />\n兩日前於柴灣青年廣場城市售票網，排隊購買劉德華演唱會門票的58歲姓鄭內地男子，與兩名操本地話男子爭執，更被其中一人用利刀襲擊，左手及左耳中刀受傷。<br />\n<br />\n東區反黑組接手調查，至今日凌晨約1時，在柴灣耀興道一單位拘捕一名26歲姓譚涉案男子。涉嫌串謀有意圖傷人，現正被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n據知譚男為黑幫新義安小頭目，人稱「拓海」，有指他當晚曾到現場，向每名排隊人士提出：「我畀你排廿個位無問題，到時留幾個位畀我。」疑被斬內地男子拒絕惹禍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180828/58615105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F58615105&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=5af89aaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F58615105&h=8888023b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180828/58615105</a><br />\n<br />\n拓海係邊位手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2bb13660285735f30fbce3e731d637dadd1ff0","tid":796650,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"拓海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cbb5dffb2977dea6ab705c33270e2c6365c43e","tid":796650,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/101130_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F101130_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9085c681&